<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Three.js on mess cat</title><link>https://messcat-38.github.io/tags/three.js/</link><description>Recent content in Three.js on mess cat</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>ja</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 Aug 2025 20:00:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://messcat-38.github.io/tags/three.js/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Geometric</title><link>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/geometric/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Aug 2025 20:00:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/geometric/</guid><description>&lt;p>Geometric series&lt;/br>
ホイールでズーム、ドラッグで回転、スライダーで比率 r と段数 N を調整できます。&lt;/p>
&lt;div id="geo-root" style="width:100%;max-width:900px;height:520px;margin:1rem auto;border:2px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3);border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0f 0%, #1e1b4b 100%);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(59,130,246,0.1);overflow:hidden">&lt;/div>
&lt;div id="geo-ui" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:1rem;background:rgba(15,23,42,0.8);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2)">
 &lt;label style="color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:500">r: &lt;input id="geo-r" type="range" min="0.5" max="0.95" step="0.005" value="0.8" style="accent-color:#3b82f6">&lt;/label>
 &lt;label style="color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:500">N: &lt;input id="geo-n" type="range" min="5" max="200" step="1" value="80" style="accent-color:#3b82f6">&lt;/label>
 &lt;span id="geo-info" style="opacity:.9;color:#94a3b8;font-family:monospace;background:rgba(59,130,246,0.1);padding:0.5rem 1rem;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2)">&lt;/span>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Julia</title><link>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/julia/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Aug 2025 15:35:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/julia/</guid><description>&lt;p>Three.js でジュリア集合を描画する。&lt;/br>
ホイールでズーム、ドラッグでパン。操作できます。&lt;/p>
&lt;div id="julia-root" style="width:100%;max-width:900px;height:520px;margin:1rem auto;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);border-radius:8px;background:#000;position:relative">&lt;/div>
&lt;div id="julia-ui" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
 &lt;label>Re(c): &lt;input id="julia-cre" type="range" min="-1" max="1" step="0.001" value="-0.8">&lt;/label>
 &lt;label>Im(c): &lt;input id="julia-cim" type="range" min="-1" max="1" step="0.001" value="0.156">&lt;/label>
 &lt;span id="julia-cval" style="opacity:.8">&lt;/span>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>pendulum</title><link>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/pendulum/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Aug 2025 15:00:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://messcat-38.github.io/posts/pendulum/</guid><description>&lt;p>Three.js で作った二重振り子。&lt;/br>
球をドラッグして初期角度を変更できます。
スペースキーで一時停止/再開。&lt;/p>
&lt;div id="dp-root" style="width:100%;max-width:900px;height:520px;margin:1rem auto;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);border-radius:8px;background:var(--dp-bg,#fff)">&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>